    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一波又一波敌人不断袭来，它们要踏平你的防线！请从商店中挑选具有不同效果的武器、增益和词条等模块并部署在战场上，以将所有敌人悉数剿灭。各个模块拥有特定的生效范围，所以你必须仔细地管理它们的位置关系并最大化效益！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202010/extras/614fb906e40006fa17b389a1aab09997.poster.avif?t=1746144287\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202010/extras/614fb906e40006fa17b389a1aab09997.webm?t=1746144287\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202010/extras/614fb906e40006fa17b389a1aab09997.mp4?t=1746144287\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 精心规划的格子管理和深思熟虑的肉鸽构筑 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 66个完全不同的模块：8种武器，18种词缀，28种属性…更多精彩内容开发中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 天赋树系统来了！准备起飞吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 游戏时长适中：单次通关游戏约1小时（你可以存档）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 包含对游戏机制的充分解释 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 与全世界玩家竞技，冲击Steam排行榜，展现你惊人的build！</p>",
